   "source": [
    "{\n",
    " \"cells\": [\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"# Headline Generator\\n\",\"**NLP Project 57 of 100** — Generate multiple headline variants for articles using templates and LLMs.\\n\",\"\\n\",\"## Learning Objectives\\n\",\"1. Use prompting for creative text generation.\\n\",\"2. Generate multiple headline variations with different tones.\\n\",\"3. Evaluate headline quality.\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"import numpy as np, pandas as pd, re, requests, json\\nimport warnings; warnings.filterwarnings('ignore')\\nprint('Loaded.')\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"ARTICLES = [\\n    'Scientists at MIT have developed a new AI model that can predict protein structures with 95% accuracy, potentially revolutionizing drug discovery.',\\n    'Global temperatures reached a record high in 2025, with scientists warning that immediate action is needed to prevent catastrophic climate change.',\\n    'The Federal Reserve announced a surprise interest rate cut, sending stock markets to all-time highs and sparking debate among economists.',\\n]\\n\\nTONES = ['Professional/Neutral', 'Clickbait/Engaging', 'Question-Style', 'Data-Driven']\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"## Template-Based Headlines\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"def extract_key_phrases(text):\\n    words = re.findall(r'\\\\b[A-Z][a-z]+(?:\\\\s[A-Z][a-z]+)*\\\\b', text)\\n    numbers = re.findall(r'\\\\d+%?', text)\\n    return words[:3], numbers[:2]\\n\\ndef generate_headlines(text):\\n    phrases, numbers = extract_key_phrases(text)\\n    subject = phrases[0] if phrases else 'Researchers'\\n    num = numbers[0] if numbers else ''\\n    headlines = [\\n        f'{subject}: New Breakthrough Changes Everything',\\n        f'Breaking: {subject} Announces Major Development',\\n        f'What {subject} Just Did Will Surprise You',\\n        f'Can {subject} Really Change the Game? Here\\\\'s What We Know',\\n    ]\\n    if num: headlines.append(f'{subject} Achieves {num} — Here\\\\'s Why It Matters')\\n    return headlines\\n\\nfor i, article in enumerate(ARTICLES):\\n    print(f'\\\\nArticle {i+1}: {article[:80]}...')\\n    for h in generate_headlines(article):\\n        print(f'  → {h}')\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"## LLM-Based Headlines (Ollama)\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"def generate_llm_headlines(text, model='qwen3:1.7b'):\\n    prompt = f'Generate 4 different headlines for this article. One professional, one engaging, one as a question, one data-driven. Output only headlines numbered 1-4.\\\\n\\\\nArticle: {text} /no_think'\\n    try:\\n        r = requests.post('http://localhost:11434/api/generate',json={'model':model,'prompt':prompt,'stream':False},timeout=60)\\n        return r.json().get('response','No response')\\n    except: return 'Ollama unavailable — use template headlines above.'\\n\\nprint(generate_llm_headlines(ARTICLES[0]))\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"## Summary\\n\",\"- **Template-based headlines are fast and reliable** for consistent formats.\\n\",\"- **LLMs produce more creative and varied headlines** but need quality filtering.\\n\",\"- **For production, generate multiple variants and A/B test** click-through rates.\\n\",\"- **Headline quality depends on capturing the key claim** of the article.\"]}\n",
    " ],\n",
